                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861025-73-off420 t17861025-73-cd421"></join> last, two guineas, value 2 l. 2 s. and nine shillings in monies numbered, and an iron japanned snuff box, value 1 d. the property of 
                     
